---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Precision Part Manufacturing — Formic"
  description="Mill, lathe, and injection-mold tending — Formic removes the hardest, most repetitive tasks from your floor."
  ogTitle="Precision Part Manufacturing"
  ogDescription="Mill / lathe machine tending and injection molding tending under Formic Full Service."
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/precision" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span>Precision Part Manufacturing
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Precision Part Manufacturing</div>
    <h1>Removing the <em>hardest tasks</em>.</h1>
    <p class="lede">Mill, lathe, and injection-mold tending — the most repetitive, dangerous, and hardest-to-staff jobs on a precision manufacturing floor, automated under Formic Full Service.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — Why It Matters</div>
      <h2>Spindle uptime is <em>everything</em>.</h2>
      <p>In precision part manufacturing, a stopped spindle is lost margin. Most shops are losing 20–40% of available spindle time to operator-bound load/unload cycles, breaks, and shift changes. Robotic tending recovers that time without adding shift coverage.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Higher spindle utilization (often 80%+ vs. 50–60% manual baseline)</li>
        <li>Consistent cycle times — no operator-driven variance</li>
        <li>Operators redeployed to higher-value setup, programming, and QC work</li>
        <li>Lights-out shifts feasible on the same equipment</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-9787.jpg" alt="Robot loading a CNC machine" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Light-out machining</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-0143.jpg" alt="Mill / lathe tending cell" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Mill · Lathe · Multi-machine</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — Mill / Lathe Tending</div>
      <h2>Light-out machining, <em>on your existing line</em>.</h2>
      <p>Robotic part loading and unloading on mills and lathes — single-machine cells, multi-machine cells, and full bays. Compatible with your existing CNCs, integrated with your existing fixtures.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Single-machine and multi-machine cells</li>
        <li>Compatible with Haas, Mazak, Okuma, DMG Mori, and other major CNC brands</li>
        <li>Vision-guided part recognition for mixed-part runs</li>
        <li>Integrated air-blast and brush-clean stations for clean handoffs</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/#cta" class="larr">Scope a cell →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">03 — Injection Molding Tending</div>
      <h2>Mold to packed, <em>hands-off</em>.</h2>
      <p>Part removal, sprue handling, post-processing, and downstream packaging integrated into one robotic cell. Consistent quality, faster cycles, fewer operator hours per part — and dramatically lower scrap from operator-induced variability.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Vertical and horizontal molding machines supported</li>
        <li>Integrated sprue separation and trim operations</li>
        <li>Direct-to-pack handoff for downstream cells</li>
        <li>Compatible with major IMM brands and gripper standards</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/#cta" class="larr">Talk to engineering →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-0095.jpg" alt="Robotic injection mold tending" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Mold tending · Post-processing</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Spindles up.<br><em>Hands off.</em></h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get Started</a>
    <a href="/" class="btn-ctawh">Back to Home</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
